ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectSpecial Economic Measures (South Sudan) Permit Authorization Order
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to issue to any person in Canada or any Canadian outside Canada a permit to carry out a specified activity or transaction, or any class of activity or transaction, that is restricted or prohibited under the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (SOUTH SUDAN) REGULATIONS.
